CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1941, pg. 18 reads: "Where Highly Competitive Pittsburgh Elks' Western Pennsylvania Open Golf Tourney Will Be Played - Pictured above are of the beautiful South Park Golf Course, where the Pittsburgh Elks' Western Pennsylvania Open Golf Tournament will be played June 17. Dave Wilson, sensational young Pittsburgher, is ...tain his title. - Harris Photo
